title: LF Help with my jungling style
body:
Hello, 

I moved back to the jungle just as pre-season started and I play for a small team around gold plat level. I seem to have decent objective control but do not seem to be able to end up as impactful as the enemy jungler about 70% of the time. 

I was hoping I could get some help to have a look into a VOD review. I did consider going to a coaching website but I think mostly I'd be keen to see if someone could do a small VOD review instead. 

Thank you, 
Here is my Discord BerserkerFury#9450. Message on there or on this thread if you would be looking to help. 
Just an hour out of your day, even if you charge I'd consider it I would just like some advice :c

replies.body: I'll do it. Link me a vid you want me to look at and I'll see what I can do.
